import React from "react";
import { Grid, Typography, FormLabel, Input } from "@material-ui/core";

export default function TravMedia() {
  return (
    <>
      <Grid
        container
        direction="column"
        justifyContent="center"
        alignItems="center"
        background="#6c63ff"
      >
        <Grid item>
          <Typography variant="h4">Axel Front End</Typography>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item>
          <Typography variant="h4">Axel Front End</Typography>
          <Typography variant="body1" component="ul">
            <Typography variant="body1" component="li">
              44 something street
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body1" component="li">
              666 666 666
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body1" component="li">
              test@test.se
            </Typography>
          </Typography>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item>
          <Typography variant="h5">Email us:</Typography>
          <form>
            <Typography>
              <FormLabel>Name:</FormLabel>
              <Input name="name" type="text"></Input>
            </Typography>
            <Typography>
              <FormLabel>Company:</FormLabel>
              <Input name="name" type="text"></Input>
            </Typography>
            <Typography>
              <FormLabel>Email:</FormLabel>
              <Input name="EmailAdress" type="email"></Input>
            </Typography>
            <Typography>
              <FormLabel>PhoneNumber:</FormLabel>
              <Input name="Phone" type="text"></Input>
            </Typography>
            <Typography>
              <FormLabel>Message:</FormLabel>
              <textArea name="message" rows="5"></textArea>
            </Typography>
          </form>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
      <Grid container></Grid>
    </>
  );
}
